title: can be input as a list of (inhomogeneous!) records
pid: ddbb3cc8-61d0-47f0-82cc-fdd069c9a744
body: |2-
  echo [ {name: sam, rank: 10},
         {name: bob, a:2, rank: 7} ]

  ╭───┬──────┬──────┬────╮
  │ # │ name │ rank │ a  │
  ├───┼──────┼──────┼────┤
  │ 0 │ sam  │   10 │ ❎ │
  │ 1 │ bob  │    7 │  2 │
  ╰───┴──────┴──────┴────╯
